{"tid":2240513,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［突發］［多圖］又有on9仔袋都唔攞就落車","createTime":"2020-10-12T16:46:17.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-13T02:55:22.000Z","uid":370483,"like":5,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"371a1c4f8ce8222f96a85c8f6fbf6f6869efb6d0","tid":2240513,"uid":370483,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-12T16:46:17.000Z","msg":"個on9仔就係我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我喺10月12號夜晚11:15左右<br />\n搭5B往堅尼地城方向<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/td6YBH5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ftd6YBH5.png&h=df656b8e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n成個袋留咗喺上層尾二排度<br />\n入面有個銀包<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/n2T8evb.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fn2T8evb.png&h=832d278c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n係呢個款<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />但唔同色<br />\n求好心人攞咗可以打俾入面間學校個電話<br />\n啲錢都由佢啦 但係啲相對我好重要<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n坐我後面個靚仔巴打如果攞咗嘅話<br />\n求下你比返啲嘢我啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好人一生平安<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"758756f7f2be9fadf70462abc84d6a2bfa079362","tid":2240513,"uid":370483,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-12T16:47:19.000Z","msg":"P牌冇力一推<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c28e5e81be54ca97b6c6484229d7cbccb0f58001","tid":2240513,"uid":370483,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-12T16:48:11.000Z","msg":"啲錢比你都可以 但啲嘢對我真係好有意義<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eea2584fc5b245716cefb8519b89f0ece242f29d","tid":2240513,"uid":252142,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-12T16:49:43.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4926d72c177cb3d68013139e2ed03c99c84fd995","tid":2240513,"uid":370483,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"eea2584fc5b245716cefb8519b89f0ece242f29d","tid":2240513,"uid":252142,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-12T16:49:43.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-12T16:50:48.000Z","msg":"咁我買返得唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我知錯喇"},{"pid":"5dc017a24ff79549a109ed8114e033e1ecd827be","tid":2240513,"uid":693,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-12T16:51:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"43f8c071d00fb268d09e0b949bc210cd5bc25645","tid":2240513,"uid":18220,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-12T16:52:09.000Z","msg":"5B 好似停西環尾招商局應該唔難搵<br />\n樓豬邊個站落車<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/sneeze.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b38e69d084470ce6cd8c1a427503c4890f2ea7e","tid":2240513,"uid":18220,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"eea2584fc5b245716cefb8519b89f0ece242f29d","tid":2240513,"uid":252142,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-12T16:49:43.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-12T16:52:32.000Z","msg":"😦"},{"pid":"775f73f82f40416bf9de89cafc837d38c3d3cf08","tid":2240513,"uid":370483,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5dc017a24ff79549a109ed8114e033e1ecd827be","tid":2240513,"uid":693,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-12T16:51:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-1